message.content: The likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are "cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.DB, cs.IR, cs.LG". The paper discusses question-answering over semi-structured data using semantic parsing and machine learning techniques. This topic falls under the intersection of several CS sub-categories, including computational linguistics (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), databases (cs.DB), information retrieval (cs.IR), and machine learning (cs.LG).
